data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a vibrant and sought-after community! This brand new listing is strategically located in a hot area, offering the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled in a highly desirable neighborhood with swim/tennis amenities, this home is a haven for families seeking an ideal lifestyle. Enjoy the added benefit of top-notch education with access to the prestigious Fulton County Schools, ensuring a quality learning environment for your children.    As you step through the front door, the grandeur of high ceilings in the foyer and living room sets a welcoming tone. Modern comfort is guaranteed with the newly installed HVAC system, providing efficient climate control. The open concept living room and kitchen create a seamless flow, making it an entertainer's dream – perfect for hosting family gatherings or social events.    Situated on one of the largest lots in the subdivision, the home boasts an expansive backyard, offering space for children to play freely and the opportunity to create your own outdoor oasis. Meticulously cared for, this property is a testament to pride of ownership, providing peace of mind for prospective buyers.    The extra-large 4th bedroom adds versatility, serving as a spacious guest room, home office, or a comfortable retreat for a growing family. Beyond being an ideal family home, this property presents itself as a great investment opportunity. With its prime location, desirable features, and impeccable maintenance, this listing is not just a home but a wise investment for someone looking to secure a valuable piece of real estate. Don't miss the chance to experience the lifestyle this home offers – schedule a showing today!
